{
  "text": "As Ra well knows, the information that we accumulate here will be illuminating to but a very modern percentage of those who populate this planet presently simply because there are very, very few people who can understand it. However, it seems that our fifth density visitor is, shall we say, dead set against this communication. Can you tell me why this is so important to him since it has such a limited effect, I would guess, upon the harvest of this planet, since it seems to me that those who will understand this information will quite possibly already be within the limits of harvestability. This constitutes an acceptance of responsibility for service to others, which is of relative purity, the instrument through which we speak and its support a group have a similar fidelity and disregarding any inconvenience to self the desire to serve others, and due to the nature of the group, the queries made to us by the group have led rapidly into somewhat abstruse regions of commentary. Such purity is as a light, such an intensity of light attracts attention.",
